Package objects

Provides classes for interest's domain.

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Flight
    Represents a flight that the company performs.
    HoldLuggage
    Represents an hold luggage.
    Insurance
    Represents an insurance.
    Meal
    Represents a meal on the airplane.
    Reservation
    Represents a reservation of one or more tickets.
    Route
    Represent a route exercised by the company.
    Seat
    Represents a booked in seat associated to a ticket.
    Ticket
    Represents a ticket associated to a one and only seat on a specific flight on an airplane.
